{"tid":2068271,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"導演李力持 fb 帳號　違反守則被封！","createTime":"2020-06-17T14:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T15:36:04.000Z","uid":105567,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"57316cbcd159649e501591e61a09bd646ed9d339","tid":2068271,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:30:13.000Z","msg":"近日多次在網上發表親建制言論的導演李力持，因為違反 fb 社群守則中，有關暴力和煽動仇恨的規定，被封鎖帳號；《蘋果日報》引述 fb 發言人指，該賬戶「多次違反多項 Facebook 社群守則」所以被停用，強調 fb 禁止用戶在平台發佈暴力、煽動犯罪或宣揚暴力的內容。<br />\n<br />\n李力持在自己另一個帳號「李大力」，上載多張截圖，顯示他原本的 fb 帳號「李力持」因違反《社群守則》規定被停用，未來 30 天不能發文或回應，他亦貼截圖指，自己一度開了一個新賬號「李力馳」，但亦在短時間內再被停用，「洗唔洗貢快呀」；他亦有將相關截圖貼在個人微博，有大陸網民留言支持，「撑你，李力持导演」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B0%8E%E6%BC%94%E6%9D%8E%E5%8A%9B%E6%8C%81-fb-%E5%B8%B3%E8%99%9F-%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E5%AE%88%E5%89%87%E8%A2%AB%E5%B0%81/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B0%258E%25E6%25BC%2594%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%258C%2581-fb-%25E5%25B8%25B3%25E8%2599%259F-%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25AE%2588%25E5%2589%2587%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25B0%2581%2F&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wbvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=eec244d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B0%258E%25E6%25BC%2594%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%258C%2581-fb-%25E5%25B8%25B3%25E8%2599%259F-%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25AE%2588%25E5%2589%2587%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25B0%2581%2F&h=112f26ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B0%8E%E6%BC%94%E6%9D%8E%E5%8A%9B%E6%8C%81-fb-%E5%B8%B3%E8%99%9F-%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E5%AE%88%E5%89%87%E8%A2%AB%E5%B0%81/</a>"},{"pid":"078c6f86252f9faa5d8d49898cf3eb2c263bd2e7","tid":2068271,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:36:04.000Z","msg":"藍絲係柒啲架啦"}]}